            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p><strong>Even Skin Tone</strong> – Targets and corrects uneven tone for a smoother, more radiant complexion.</p><p><strong>Glass Glow Effect</strong> – Firms, lifts, and enhances facial contours for a youthful, glowing look.</p><p><strong>Instant Benefits</strong> – Achieve the Korean \"glass skin\" glow with tightened, radiant skin. Silicone-free, low-irritating, dermatologist-tested.</p><p><strong>Key Ingredients</strong> – <em>Hydrolyzed Collagen</em> improves elasticity and absorption; <em>Niacinamide</em> strengthens the skin barrier and hydrates for better texture.</p><p><strong>Clinically Tested</strong> and <strong>Dermatologist approved.</strong></p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_QnkEdx": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How does it work?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>You may use the Neck Tightening Cream daily.</p><p>It is designed for both morning and evening use as part of your skincare routine. The rich yet non-greasy formula contains key ingredients like Cupuaçu Butter, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid, and Caffeine, which work together to boost collagen, deeply hydrate, and improve skin firmness and elasticity.</p><p>To maximize its effectiveness, apply it daily after cleansing and before sunscreen in the morning, and as the last step in your evening routine.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_WYG8GJ": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use it for sensitive skin?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes! All skin types, including sensitive skin.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_kwzWVt": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Ingredients",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>We do not include any harmful parabens or other nasties. We also NEVER test on animals.</p><p><strong>Cupuacu Butter - </strong>It hydrates and firms the neck while protecting skin from dryness.<br/><br/><strong>Matribust - </strong>Helps firm and lift the neck and chest area by improving skin elasticity and strengthening support fibers.<br/><br/><strong>Hydrolized HyaluronicAcid - </strong>Deeply hydrates the skin, plumps fine lines, and improves elasticity for a smoother, firmer appearance.<br/><br/><strong>Caffeine - </strong>Helps reduce puffiness, tighten skin, and improve circulation for a firmer, more toned appearance.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_QGc8Kr": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Shipping & Delivery",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p><strong>Processing Time:</strong><br/>Once your order is placed, please allow 24 hours for us to process and prepare your order for shipment.<br/><br/><strong>Shipping Time:</strong><br/>After your order is dispatched, it will typically take 4-8 business days to reach you, depending on your location.<br/><br/><strong>Tracking Information:</strong><br/>Once your order has been shipped, you will receive an email containing your tracking number. You can use this to track your package and stay updated on its delivery status.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_8h6X4m": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Return & Exchange Policy",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>We want you to be fully satisfied with your purchase! If you are not completely happy with your order, we accept returns and exchanges within 60 days from the date of purchase.<br/><br/>Contact us via the website or via email: info@niforashop.com</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
