    "custom_liquid_fbTAUw": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "disabled": true,
      "settings": {
        "display_id": false,
        "visibility": "always-display",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"product__block product__features\" data-slider=\"\" style=\"--PBB:20px;\">\n  <div class=\"product__feature\" data-block-id=\"feature_A3b4kT\">\n    <div class=\"product__feature__content\">\n      <div class=\"product__feature__icon__container\">\n        <!-- Main Headline -->\n        <div class=\"product__feature__headline\">\n          <h3>TRY US RISK FREE</h3>\n        </div>\n        <!-- Subheadline -->\n        <div class=\"product__feature__heading\">\n          <h5><strong>60-Day Money-Back Guarantee</strong></h5>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"product__feature__text\">\n        <p><br>We're confident you'll love <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>our Neck Tightening Cream.</strong></span>  If for any reason you're not satisfied or don't see visible improvement in your skin, we'll refund your order - no questions asked.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n  /* Minimalist background for the block */\n  .product__feature {\n    background: #f7f7f7; /* Soft light gray */\n    padding: 20px;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    box-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); /* Very subtle shadow */\n    border: 1px solid #eaeaea; /* Light border for definition */\n    max-width: 450px; /* Keeps it clean */\n    margin: auto; /* Centers the block horizontally */\n    text-align: left; /* Ensures everything is left-aligned */\n  }\n\n  /* Main Headline */\n  .product__feature__headline h3 {\n    font-size: 26px;\n    font-weight: bold;\n    color: #000;\n    margin-bottom: 5px;\n    text-align: left; /* Left align */\n  }\n\n  /* Subheadline */\n  .product__feature__heading h5 {\n    font-size: 18px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #8b1638;\n    text-transform: none; /* Capitalizes only the first letters */\n    margin: 0;\n    text-align: left; /* Left align */\n  }\n\n  /* Text content */\n  .product__feature__text p {\n    font-size: 16px;\n    color: #000;\n    line-height: 24px;\n    text-align: left; /* Left align */\n  }\n\n  /* Mobile adjustments */\n  @media (max-width: 500px) {\n    .product__feature {\n      padding: 15px;\n      max-width: 100%;\n    }\n\n    .product__feature__headline h3 {\n      font-size: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .product__feature__heading h5 {\n      font-size: 15px;\n    }\n\n    .product__feature__text p {\n      font-size: 15px;\n      line-height: 22px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>",
        "color_scheme": "background-1",
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 0
      }
    },
    "ss_product_ingredients_6_LwRdjx": {
      "type": "ss-product-ingredients-6",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_jBWkcx": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<p><strong>Every Ingredient Carefully Chosen</strong></p>",
            "heading_custom": false,
            "heading_font": "poppins_n7",
            "heading_size": 36,
            "heading_size_mobile": 32,
            "heading_height": 130,
            "heading_mt": 0,
            "heading_mt_mobile": 0,
            "heading_color": "#8b1638"
          }
        },
        "text_4eti3z": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Each ingredient in our <strong>Neck Tightening Cream</strong> is carefully chosen and backed by science—not empty claims. We avoid harsh fillers and hidden additives—just a clean, effective formula powered by <strong>clinically supported ingredients</strong> like <strong>cupuacu butter, hyaluronic acid, matribust, and caffeine</strong> to visibly firm, smooth, and hydrate delicate neck skin. Because real results start with real ingredients.</p>",
            "text_custom": false,
            "text_font": "josefin_sans_n4",
            "text_size": 13,
            "text_size_mobile": 13,
            "text_height": 130,
            "text_mt": 4,
            "text_mt_mobile": 12,
            "text_color": "#121212"
          }
        },
        "card_AkeN33": {
          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/3_2c4def87-65d7-444b-9611-0b999848b8ea.png",
            "title": "Cupuacu Butter",
            "text": "<p>Deep hydration</p>",
            "source": "",
            "modal_text": "<p>Our Neck Tightening Cream is enriched with <strong>Cupuacu Butter</strong> — a plant-based emollient derived from the seeds of the Cupuacu fruit. Known for its exceptional water-retention abilities, it delivers <strong>deep, long-lasting hydration</strong> while strengthening the skin barrier. Rich in phytosterols and fatty acids, Cupuacu Butter helps <strong>restore elasticity, improve skin softness</strong>, and protect against environmental stress—making it ideal for nourishing and smoothing delicate neck skin.<br/><br/></p>",
            "modal_subtitle": "",
            "modal_sub_text": "",
            "url": ""
          }
        },
        "card_h7zJ7G": {
          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Hyaluronix.png",
            "title": "Hyaluronic Acid",
            "text": "<p>Boosts Skin Hydration</p>",
            "source": "",
            "modal_text": "<p><strong>Hyaluronic acid </strong>is a moisture-binding ingredient that <strong>deeply hydrates the skin</strong>, helping it appear plump, smooth, and supple. It holds up to 1,000 times its weight in water,<strong> supporting skin elasticity</strong> and <strong>reducing the look of fine lines</strong>. In the Bio-Collagen Mask, it enhances absorption and boosts the mask’s firming and rejuvenating effects.</p>",
            "modal_subtitle": "",
            "modal_sub_text": "",
            "url": ""
          }
        },
        "card_9f4MdD": {
          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2_fa174842-0238-407e-be80-a05e9a3a0607.png",
            "title": "Matribust",
            "text": "<p>Lifting support</p>",
            "source": "",
            "modal_text": "<p><strong>Matribust</strong> is an advanced firming complex designed to <strong>restructure and tone</strong> the delicate skin of the neck and décolleté. It stimulates <strong>collagen and elastin production</strong>, helping to <strong>lift sagging skin</strong>, improve elasticity, and restore density. With consistent use, it visibly enhances skin firmness and smoothness—supporting a more defined, youthful-looking neckline.</p>",
            "modal_subtitle": "",
            "modal_sub_text": "",
            "url": ""
          }
        },
        "card_YBm4PF": {
          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1_f241c91a-dac7-4596-b2de-7356e06c7297.png",
            "title": "Caffeine",
            "text": "<p>Firming boost</p>",
            "source": "",
            "modal_text": "<p><strong>Caffeine </strong>is a skin-energizing ingredient known for its ability to <strong>firm, tighten, and revitalize</strong>. It stimulates microcirculation, which helps reduce puffiness and improves skin tone. By constricting blood vessels, it temporarily tightens the skin, giving a smoother, more lifted appearance. Caffeine also provides antioxidant protection, helping to defend against environmental stressors. In the Neck Tightening Cream, it works to <strong>enhance firmness</strong>, reduce visible fatigue, and promote a more sculpted, youthful-looking neckline.</p>",
            "modal_subtitle": "",
            "modal_sub_text": "",
            "url": ""
          }
        },
        "card_YDVTYq": {
          "type": "card",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Glycerin.png",
            "title": "Glycerin",
            "text": "<p>Moisture Lock</p>",
            "source": "",
            "modal_text": "<p><strong>Glycerin </strong>is a powerful humectant that draws moisture into the skin and <strong>helps maintain hydration levels</strong>. It works to soften rough patches, improve skin elasticity, and support the skin’s natural barrier. In the Bio-Collagen Mask, it helps lock in moisture,<strong> keeping the skin plump</strong>, smooth, and comfortable during and after use.</p>",
            "modal_subtitle": "",
            "modal_sub_text": "",
            "url": ""
          }
        },
        "card_HT3DHU": {
          "type": "card",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Galactomyces.png",
            "title": "Galactomyces",
            "text": "<p>Radiance Booster</p>",
            "source": "",
            "modal_text": "<p><strong>Galactomyces</strong> is a fermented yeast extract rich in vitamins, amino acids, and antioxidants that <strong>help nourish and revitalize the skin</strong>. It works to improve skin clarity, <strong>refine pores</strong>, and balance sebum production. It <strong>enhances radiance</strong>, <strong>smooths texture</strong>, and supports a brighter, more even complexion.<br/></p>",
            "modal_subtitle": "",
            "modal_sub_text": "",
            "url": ""
          }
        },
